      "writtenOn": "2017-08-01T21:27:29Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "If you were to add the Semaphore, that’d make three statics here, and at that point, it may become worthwhile to make TimerTest an object that carries timer_, event_, and the semaphore as nonstatic data members. Then you’d just have a static TimerTest* pointing to the active timer so that you had access to it from the static HandleTimer().",
